features: IPX8 Certified CACOE Waterproof Case：With the excellent IPX8 waterproof seal, this 100% waterproof phone case protects the devices in a variety of environments. The maximum water depth is 30m, it features easy snap and lock access that ensures a perfect seal. Protects against water, snow, dust, sand and dirt.(NOTE: Please test underwater before use).

Upgraded Universal Waterproof Phone Case: Suitable for smartphones under 7.0 inches. Using TPU material, it has high transparency and more sensitive touch, which is very convenient for taking pictures, watching videos and reading information. (Some large-screen mobile phones need to remove the protective case)
Upgraded Floating Function: Four-sided double airbags for stronger buoyancy,prevent your phone from sinking into the water.

Upgraded Seal Tech：All-new snap-and-lock seal clip and fully-enclosed rim help waterproof phone case keep your phone well protected from water intruders for beach, pool, fishing, swimming, boating, kayaking, snorkeling and water park activities.

Please note：1. This waterproof cell phone case is not for use with thick case cell phones. 2. Due to the water pressure and water temperature below a certain depth, it may affect the function of the cell phone, such as the touch screen. In such a case, please press the volume button to take a picture. 3. Face ID and Home button function are affected (maximum water depth is 30m).

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Notice: 1. Mobile phones with thick covers are not recommended for this bag! 2. Do not insert sharp objects into the waterproof bag! 3. The mobile phone may suffer from water pressure below a certain depth, which affects the operation of the touch screen. In this case, please take photos using the volume buttons. 4. When the water temperature drops and the phone temperature rises, fogging of the inside of the phone case is quite normal. 5. Please do a safety check before use. Follow the steps for use by inserting a paper tissue into the waterproof case and placing the waterproof phone case in water for 30 minutes. Then take it out to check if the tissue is wet. If the tissue is wet, do not use the Waterproof Phone Case and notify us immediately for a replacement.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Yes it's waterproof and floatable!!!
reviews.reviewText: I looked around online for a waterproof case and I'm glad I got this one. No regrets at all!This case worked very well and kept my phone dry during our 3 day lake trip. It's 100% waterproof and floatable as in the ad. I swam with the phone and put the phone upside down in the water and not a single drop came inside the case.The photos and videos are very clear and beautiful as if there was no cover on the phone. The case doesn't bother scrolling and swiping either. So I just kept the phone in the case all day except while it was being charged.The water would block the touchscreen so I started the video above the water and submerged the phone in the water to take images underwater.When I placed the phone in the case, I made sure 1. To remove as much air as possible from between the phone and the case, 2. There is no wrinkles or sand etc on the case especially around the opening, 3. To press the plastic pieces firmly and lock the case. It takes only 15 seconds!!I'm so happy I can finally take photos and videos in the water without a fear of getting my phone wet and broken. I would recommend this and would buy this again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I am sooo amazed by this ! I thought there could be a chance of water getting in to some extent but it really stayed dry throughout my Cancun vacation!!! Beaches, cenotes, swimming pool- took them everywhere and my 11 yr old son was able to use it independantly too! Had a bad experience with another brand that I cannot even remember now but this product is great quality! The straps are strong, plastic is thick , roomy for large phones too and its easy to seal ur phone in! Ooh I was also texting my husband while in the pool without needing to open the case (like one liners not too long though) LOVE LOVE LOVE IT! One of my best Amazon purchases (I have had bad luck on so many !)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Sank straight to the creek bottom!!!
reviews.reviewText: I’m not sure what everyone had in theirs when they “floated”, but I flipped my paddle board in the creek today and to my horror mine sank straight to the bottom of Econfina creek. Thankfully the water was clear and we were able to keep circling back against the current until I found it lying on the bottom right where I turned over. Will not float with IPhone 14 pro max inside!!!!! I’m still giving it 3 stars because the phone inside was in fact DRY.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Used these on a boat ride. I was happy with the picture quality through the case. I was comforted that if I dropped it off the boat, I would be able to retrieve it.

My friend and I tested it at the hotel before we went in the waves (i suggest you do the same just in case) and honestly I felt super safe to leave my phone and my cards and money around my neck knowing no water would get in. It worked perfectly. It's a great product, the touch screen works about 80% of the time. The best thing is that you get one and you can give one to your best friend!
